hopobject.body: Could you tell me my balance, please? www.aspenpharma.com vacancies The Last Banquet isn’t Grimwood’s first book; over the past 16 years, under the name Jon Courtenay Grimwood, he has written several excellent science-fiction and fantasy novels set in far-flung locales from an alternative-history Alexandria to a future Japan. But since The Last Banquet “is not fantastical, apart from the fact that Jean-Marie eats everything and has a tiger that lives for a long time and is essentially the spirit of the times”, the pseudonym was chosen to set it apart.
